{"tid":2447990,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"灣仔瀛豐放題食物中毒個案增至7宗　涉及18人","createTime":"2021-03-15T14:50:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T13:47:09.000Z","uid":20272,"like":74,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"3dc848811de0171ba1f3e76c860434b5b03e2a61","tid":2447990,"uid":20272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:50:54.000Z","msg":"灣仔瀛豐放題食物中毒個案增至7宗 涉及18人<br />\n灣仔京都廣場的「瀛豐放題料理專門店」，新增5宗食物中毒個案，總數增至7宗，涉及18人。 衛生防護中心表示，新增的5宗個案，涉及7男6女，年齡10至50歲，先後在本月5至12日期間在餐廳用膳，之後出現腹瀉、發燒、噁心及嘔吐等病徵。當中6人曾經求醫，毋須入院，全部人情況穩定。 防護中心流行病學調查顯示，當中4宗個案，在食環署開始調查和採取控制措施前，已在相關食肆進餐。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2383083\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2383083&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDtMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=c285c51b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2383083</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static6.orstatic.com/userphoto2/photo/1G/15MU/0882EX9134C8AB2DEE539Bpx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic6.orstatic.com%2Fuserphoto2%2Fphoto%2F1G%2F15MU%2F0882EX9134C8AB2DEE539Bpx.jpg&h=35675663&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static7.orstatic.com/userphoto2/photo/13/V3J/06553M9F15E29CB6966BCApx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic7.orstatic.com%2Fuserphoto2%2Fphoto%2F13%2FV3J%2F06553M9F15E29CB6966BCApx.jpg&h=56f4b270&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好彩咁耐以黎無因為佢係黃而去試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一直以黎見到佢件帶子夾住d海膽都好不安<br />\n<br />\n幾個月前有連登仔爆料但俾人屌返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr